title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
OB: While in the query result page, there is no data returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should display in the 'Edit Data Set' dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the 'Edit Data Set' dialog.
SR: To reproduce the issue, follow these steps: 1. Call the stored procedure from Oracle database. 2. Check the query result stored in the output parameter as an object.
